OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FScattered showers on Tuesday, with
OL,7,Fthunderstorms possible in the north.
OL,8,FLargely dry thereafter with sunny
OL,9,Fspells, although showery outbreaks of
OL,10,Frain are possible at times. Feeling
OL,11,Ffresher than of late.
